{"ts": "2026-06-08T05:01:33.077936+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 8d71d8125861b72e1904d79cc9bbad3ab2ce83d4)", "id": "lc_abe68b48-b293-41d5-ae64-eeb5a4576917"}, {"type": "text", "text": "FROM python:3.10-slim as base\n\n# Create a non-root user to run the app with.\nRUN groupadd --gid 1000 user &&  adduser --disabled-password --gecos '' --uid 1000 --gid 1000 user\nUSER user\n\nWORKDIR /home/user/app\n\n# Install Poetry.\nRUN --mount=type=cache,target=/root/.cache pip install --user poetry==1.4.2\nENV \\\n    PATH=\"/home/user/.local/bin:/home/user/app/.venv/bin:${PATH}\" \\\n    PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1 \\\n    POETRY_NO_INTERACTION=1 \\\n    POETRY_VIRTUALENVS_IN_PROJECT=true\n\nCOPY --chown=user:user ./pyproject.toml ./poetry.lock ./alembic.ini ./\nRUN --mount=type=cache,target=/root/.cache poetry install\n\nFROM base as dev\n\nCOPY --chown=user:user ./api api\n\nCMD [\"uvicorn\", \"api.main:app\", \"--host\", \"0.0.0.0\", \"--port\", \"5000\", \"--reload\"]\n\n\nFROM base as test\n\nUSER root\nRUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends git-core\nUSER user\n\nRUN --mount=type=cache,target=/root/.cache poetry install --with dev\n\n# For running pre-commit\nCOPY --chown=user:user ./.git .git\nCOPY --chown=user:user ./.pre-commit-config.yaml .pre-commit-config.yaml\n\nRUN mkdir /home/user/.mypy_cache && chown -R user:user /home/user/.mypy_cache\nRUN pre-commit install --install-hooks\n\nCOPY --chown=user:user ./api api\n\n# Default target.\nFROM dev\n", "id": "lc_b8b0c4d4-ccae-4379-9d08-fc2317d7a521"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "8774464a-4e77-490a-bf37-ee90973eb731", "tool_call_id": "call_00_HfRK6pfofIWh2nYtDSRN4822", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-08T05:01:46.313108+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "## How to Start this FastAPI Project Locally with Docker\n\n### Prerequisites\n- **Docker** and **Make** must be installed on your machine. No other local dependencies (Python, Poetry, etc.) are required.\n\n### 1. Clone and Start the Application\n\n```sh\ngit clone <repository-url>\ncd <repository-directory>\nmake up\n```\n\nThe `make up` command runs:\n```sh\ndocker compose up -d --build api\n```\n\nThis does the following:\n- Builds the `api` Docker image using the multi-stage `Dockerfile` located at `api/Dockerfile`.\n- Starts a **PostgreSQL 14.5** database container (`db`) with password `test` (exposed on `127.0.0.1:5432`).\n- Starts the **FastAPI** application container (`api`) on `http://127.0.0.1:5000` (with live reload enabled via `--reload`).\n- The app's database connection string is automatically configured as `postgresql://postgres:test@db:5432/postgres` via the `DB_STRING` environment variable set in `docker-compose.yml`.\n- The `api/` source directory is mounted as a volume, so local code changes are reflected immediately without rebuilding.\n\nOnce running, the API documentation is available at: [http://localhost:5000/docs](http://localhost:5000/docs)\n\n---\n\n### 2. Apply Database Migrations\n\nIn a separate terminal (while the containers are running), run:\n\n```sh\nmake migrate\n```\n\nThis executes:\n```sh\ndocker compose run --rm api alembic upgrade head\n```\n\nThis runs **Alembic** inside the `api` container to apply all pending database migrations (located in `api/migrations/`) against the PostgreSQL database.\n\n---\n\n### Additional Make Targets for Migrations\n\n| Command | Action |\n|---------|--------|\n| `make migrate` | Apply all pending migrations (`alembic upgrade head`) |\n| `make migrations m=\"<message>\" revid=\"<revid>\"` | Auto-generate a new migration file (e.g., `make migrations m=\"add users table\" revid=\"0002\"`) |\n| `make downgrade` | Roll back the last migration (`alembic downgrade -1`) |\n\n###\n\n", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 717, "prompt_tokens": 9365, "total_tokens": 10082, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 226, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 8832}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 8832, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 533}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-pro", "system_fingerprint": "fp_9954b31ca7_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "01f4a4ed-b43b-480b-9fee-88b30c1edf67", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea59b-8417-7e42-8759-2dbf6a692c00-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 9365, "output_tokens": 717, "total_tokens": 10082, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 8832}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 226}}}}]}}}
